# Index qa-docs/

## Statistik (2026-06-25 manifest)

| Item | Nilai |
|------|-------|
| Menu terdaftar | **121** slug di `qa-docs/_meta/manifest.yaml` |
| Folder menu | 1:1 dengan slug manifest |
| Modul | SupplyChain 55 · Accounting 42 · OmniChannel 12 · GeneralSetting 6 · Gate 4 · AI 2 |
| Status per layer doc | pending 122 · draft 217 · review 25 |

## Pohon folder

```
qa-docs/
├── README.md                 ← overview repo (bukan sumber per-menu)
├── _meta/                    ← jangan kutip ke user; manifest boleh dibaca agent
│   ├── manifest.yaml         ← SOURCE OF TRUTH index menu
│   ├── manifest-gate-gs-draft.yaml  ← snippet historis, bukan SoT
│   ├── MERMAID_STYLE_GUIDE.md
│   └── templates/            ← kb · requirement · technical · e2e-test-case
├── _legacy/                  ← referensi lama; BUKAN canonical
├── Debug *.xlsx              ← abaikan untuk jawaban
└── {menu-slug}/
    ├── README.md             ← indeks layer + route + legacy
    ├── knowledge-base.md     ← operator, support, ops
    ├── requirement.md        ← PM, QA, support
    ├── technical.md          ← developer
    └── test-cases/           ← opsional (2 menu saat ini)
        ├── README.md
        └── TC-*.md
```

## Schema entry manifest (per menu)

```yaml
{slug}:
  menu_name: "Display Name"
  path: {slug}                    # = nama folder
  module: OmniChannel|Accounting|SupplyChain|Gate|GeneralSetting|AI
  menu_links: [fe/route/segment]  # mapping URL staging
  owner: QA - Yemima
  docs:
    knowledge-base: { file, status }
    requirement:    { file, status }
    technical:      { file, status }
    test_cases:     { path, status }   # opsional
  legacy_sources: [_legacy/...]
  code_globs:       # referensi repo app — tidak ada di repo ini
    backend: [...]
    frontend: [...]
```

## Pola slug → modul

| Prefix / pola | Modul | Contoh |
|---------------|-------|--------|
| `omni-*` | OmniChannel | `omni-picking-process` |
| `accounting-*` | Accounting | `accounting-customer-invoice` |
| `supplychain-*` | SupplyChain | `supplychain-purchase-order` |
| `gate-*` | Gate | `gate-user` |
| `generalsetting-*` | GeneralSetting | `generalsetting-country` |
| `ai-*`, `kb-*` | AI | `ai-kb-assistant`, `kb-store-monitor` |
| Tanpa prefix (legacy naming) | lihat manifest | `journal`, `general-ledger`, `system-product`, `bill-of-material`, `sales-order-general`, `manage-platform-product`, `random-sku`, `sidebar-menu` |

## Workflow lookup (wajib)

1. **Cari slug** — grep `manifest.yaml` by: `menu_name`, `menu_links`, atau teks user → keyword slug
2. **Buka** `qa-docs/{slug}/README.md`
3. **Pilih layer** by audience (lihat `09-menu-documentation.mdc`)
4. **Cross-menu concept** → `random-sku/` (bukan satu menu app)
5. **Sidebar kosong / menu hilang** → `sidebar-menu/technical.md` (status `final`)
6. **Test case E2E** → cek manifest `test_cases:` dulu:
   - `accounting-customer-payment/test-cases/`
   - `generalsetting-general-company/test-cases/`

## URL staging dari menu_links

Base: `https://staging.olshoperp.com/{menu_links}`

Contoh: `menu_links: [accounting/journal]` → `/accounting/journal`

## Frontmatter per doc_type

| doc_type | Field khas |
|----------|------------|
| `knowledge-base` | `audience`, `sections` |
| `requirement` | § acceptance criteria, AS-IS |
| `technical` | `related_docs`, architecture, file map |
| `e2e-test-case` | `tc_code`, `steps`, `expected_result`, `related_menus` |

## Yang diabaikan saat indexing jawaban

- `_legacy/**`, `_meta/templates/**`, `manifest-gate-gs-draft.yaml`
- Skill/path lama `docs/qa-docs/` atau `.cursor/skills/` dari referensi docs
- `code_globs` — hanya petunjuk repo app, bukan bukti perilaku
